        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Break the ice]]></title>
            <link>https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice</link>
            <guid>https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice</guid>
            <pubDate>Sat, 28 Jun 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[의미]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="의미">의미<a href="https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice#%EC%9D%98%EB%AF%B8" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 의미" title="Direct link to 의미">​</a></h3>
<p><code>Break the ice</code>는 어색하거나 긴장된 분위기를 깨고 편안하게 만드는 것을 의미합니다.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="설명">설명<a href="https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice#%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 설명" title="Direct link to 설명">​</a></h3>
<p>처음 만난 사람들과 대화를 시작하거나, 조용하고 어색한 상황에서 분위기를 부드럽게 만들 때 사용하는 표현입니다.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="예문">예문<a href="https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice#%EC%98%88%EB%AC%B8" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 예문" title="Direct link to 예문">​</a></h3>
<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info admonition_rEt0 alert alert--info"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>info</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>At the party, John told a funny story to break the ice.</strong><br>
(파티에서 John은 어색한 분위기를 깨기 위해 재미있는 이야기를 했다.)</p></div></div>
<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info admonition_rEt0 alert alert--info"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>info</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>The teacher played a game to break the ice on the first day of class.</strong><br>
(선생님은 첫 수업 날에 어색한 분위기를 깨기 위해 게임을 했다.)</p></div></div>
<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info admonition_rEt0 alert alert--info"><div class="admonitionHeading_wRFJ"><span class="admonitionIcon_QRAt"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>info</div><div class="admonitionContent_Aoao"><p><strong>A good joke can help break the ice when meeting new people.</strong><br>
(새로운 사람을 만날 때 좋은 농담은 어색함을 풀어줄 수 있다.)</p></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Fogf" id="유사한-영어-표현">유사한 영어 표현<a href="https://your-docusaurus-site.example.com/blog/break-the-ice#%EC%9C%A0%EC%82%AC%ED%95%9C-%EC%98%81%EC%96%B4-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 유사한 영어 표현" title="Direct link to 유사한 영어 표현">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Get the ball rolling</strong></li>
<li><strong>Start the conversation</strong></li>
<li><strong>Warm up the atmosphere</strong></li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
